H3.text: Which British city has cathedrals dedicated to St Nicholas and St Mary. NuT

A4.text: Newcastle has three cathedrals, the Anglican St Nicholas', with its elegant lantern tower of 1474, the Roman Catholic St Mary's designed by Augustus Welby Pugin and the Coptic Orthodox Cathedral in Fenham.
